 Stock Market Data Analysis

This project analyzes stock data using probability and statistics.

Concepts Used
- Mean, Median, Standard Deviation
- Z-Test
- Volatility Analysis
- Rolling Mean

 Output Example

Mean: 1512.94  
Median: 1170.36  
